<H3> <TI>   Sharma, Czech President Meet, Hold News Conference </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK0802164194 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 
GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0802164194 </F>
